      decoration: BoxDecoration(color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.65), shape: BoxShape.circle),
      child: Icon(
        isLiked ? Icons.favorite : Icons.favorite_border,
        color: isLiked ? Colors.red : Colors.grey,
        size: 18,
      ),
    ),
  ),
),

